# API & Handler Conventions

## Handler Pattern

```rust
// ✅ Thin handler
async fn get_user(
    State(state): State<AppState>,
    Path(id): Path<Uuid>,
    RequireAuth(user): RequireAuth,
) -> Result<Json<UserResponse>, ApiError> {
    let user = state.user_service.get_by_id(id).await?;
    Ok(Json(user.into()))
}
```

- Extract input (path, query, body, auth)
- Call service; propagate errors with `?`
- Map domain → response at boundary

